2.3 Policies, Strategies and Frameworks Supporting KeSQAF
The development and implementation of KeSQAF is supported by various legal frameworks, strategies, policies, procedures and statistical quality frameworks. These include the:
a. Statistics Act, 2006;
b. Kenya Strategy for Development of Statistics (KSDS);
c. ISO 9001:2015 standards;
d. Existing Data Quality Assessment Frameworks (DQAFs);
e. United Nations National Quality Assurance Framework (UN-NQAF);
f. UN Principles Governing International Statistical Activities;
g. African Charter on Statistics;
h. International Statistical Institute’s (ISI) Declaration on Professional Ethics;
i. Statistical Data and Metadata Exchange (SDMX);
j. European Statistics (Eurostat) Code of Practice (CoP).
